text:
Water Management (Watercourse Authority Exemption) Amendment Order 2011 (Rescinded)

This Statutory Rule has been rescinded.

1. (Rescinded)
    The Water Management (Watercourse Authority Exemption) Amendment Order 2011 have been rescinded by Schedule 3 to the Redundant Legislation Repeal Act 2016
